    MAPSMOBCORE-11215 Prevent cURL from waiting for resolve on request finish
    
    This is the copy of https://github.com/curl/curl/pull/4882, which cURL developers do not want to merge because it interferes with Badger's dreams.
    Why does MapKit need it: this behavoiur indirectly causes MAPSMOBCORE-11215, and there is no other good way to fix this.
    
    Pros:
    1) If something is wrong with DNS (e.g. the operator is dropping DNS packets with certain hostnames), your network thread won't inevitably block like it does right now
    2) May increase overall performance if you do a lot of DNS requests
    3) Will probably end the suffering of millions of Ukranian and Russian users who experience MAPSMOBCORE-11215
    
    Cons:
    1) Never commited to cURL or tested globally, which means high risk of bugs
    2) Might conflict with future cURL releases since it will never be merged
    
    REVIEW: 1337929

